hi,

I have following problem. I was testing two diffrent lines of code:

1. return Task.WhenAll(queryTasks).Result.SelectMany(result => result);  
2. return queryTasks.Select(t => t.Result).SelectMany(r => r);

Surprisingly it looks like the second one has much better performance then the first one. I know that the first line is not recommended, because WhenAll is for await purposes, but anyway, why it has so much worse performance?

Best regards!
